      "content": "hey so im currently on sertraline (zoloft) for my anxiety but the side effects r making me feel super nauseous and weirdly restless all the time. i really wanna get off the meds but i saw online that st johns wort is basically the same thing just more natural. do u think i can just swap my zoloft for st johns wort starting tomorrow??",
